data.description: Huge corner lot, with a truly uniquely styled house. With two carports on either side with exterior doors in each, plus additional parking pads off Smith Ave. Great backyard, with privacy fencing contains a large garden shed and a deck at the back door. The double sized front room, leads into the tiled kitchen and laundry/pantry combo. Through the kitchen is a dining room with access to the back deck and main hallway. Off the main hallway there are 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This well maintained 1800+ square foot home is ready for new owners!
